  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Timber transformation event: two oak logs assembled into one dining table.",
    "eventTime IS the transformation date — no separate eudr:transformationDate is needed.",
    "masterDataAvailableFor carries GS1 product master data for inputs and output,",
    "plus product-level eudr: attributes (commodityType / timberProductType /",
    "speciesScientificName / CommonName) on each product entry — those describe the GTIN.",
    "No ilmd: we have no lot-specific data to assert for this example.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: eudr=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/eudr/",
    "See: extensions/common/core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
